-----------   создать wallet 

orapki wallet create -wallet /home/oracle/wallet -pwd password123 -auto_login

-------------  добавить certificates

orapki wallet add -wallet /home/oracle/wallet -trusted_cert -cert verisignclass3.cer -pwd password123

-----------   удалить wallet 

 orapki wallet remove -wallet /app/oracle/product/12.2.0/db/wallet -trusted_cert_all -pwd password123

-----------------  посмотертеть

orapki wallet display -wallet  /app/oracle/product/12.2.0/db/wallet
